"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel's military attacked Hezbollah targets after warning residents it would act strongly against the group.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Attacks Hezbollah\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Israel atac\u00f3 objetivos de Hezbollah despu\u00e9s de advertir a los residentes que actuar\u00eda fuertemente contra el grupo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel Ataca a Hezbollah\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Nine people were hurt and nine others are missing after a tank broke at a paper mill in Longview, Washington. Rescuers are still looking for two villagers who are missing.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tank Breaks at Paper Mill\",            \"translated_version\": \"Nueve personas resultaron heridas y nueve m\u00e1s est\u00e1n desaparecidas despu\u00e9s de que un tanque se rompi\u00f3 en una f\u00e1brica de papel en Longview, Washington. Los rescatistas todav\u00eda buscan a dos aldeanos que est\u00e1n desaparecidos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tanque Roto en F\u00e1brica de Papel\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Hamas says Mohammed Odeh, his wife, and two children were killed in a strike on a residential building.\",            \"english_title\": \"Family Killed in Strike\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hamas dice que Mohammed Odeh, su esposa y dos hijos murieron en un ataque a un edificio residencial.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Familia Muerta en Ataque\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Italian Supreme Court turned down a tourist's claim that her consumer rights were violated when she was only offered \u20ac7 bottled mineral water.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tourist's Claim Rejected\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Corte Suprema de Italia rechaz\u00f3 la queja de una turista que dec\u00eda que sus derechos de consumidor fueron violados cuando solo le ofrecieron agua mineral embotellada de 7 euros.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rechazo a Queja de Turista\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US is pulling out of trilateral talks with Russia and Ukraine, and the EU is searching for potential candidates to take part.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Leaves Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Estados Unidos se retira de las conversaciones trilaterales con Rusia y Ucrania, y la UE busca candidatos potenciales para participar.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EEUU Deja Conversaciones\"        }    ]}"